snippet.title: Virtua Cop gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Virtua Cop (aka virtua squad), PC game produced by SEGA in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/virtua-cop/2243/
Playing through the first stage of this rail shooter arcade game made by Sega.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Virtua Cop 2 - https://youtu.be/mQPZQH9VaYo
